==English==
===Noun===
'''knuckleball''' (plural: knuckleballs)

# A hard to predict event
#: Our vendor keeps throwing us '''knuckleballs'''.''
#{{baseball}} A [[pitch]] thrown with the ball gripped on the fingertips and released with no rotation which travels over a unpredictable path to the plate due to micro-turbulance in the air 
#: ''Even the pitcher doesn't know where his '''knuckleball''' is going.''

